```sparql
PREFIX cvx: <https://knacc.umbc.edu/dae-young/kim/ontologies/synthea#hl7:CVX>
PREFIX udi: <https://knacc.umbc.edu/dae-young/kim/ontologies/synthea#fda:UDI>

PREFIX loinc: <https://knacc.umbc.edu/dae-young/kim/ontologies/synthea#loinc:LOINC>

SELECT ?procedure
WHERE {
  ?patient a syn:Patient;
        syn:hasDiagnosis ?diagnosis.
  ?diagnosis a syn:Diagnosis;
        syn:hasFinding ?finding.
  ?finding syn:hasCode ?code.
  FILTER (
    CONCAT(str(?code), ' (', str(?diagnosis), ')') = 'Mold (organism)'

  ?patient syn:receivedProcedure ?procedure.
  GROUP BY ?procedure
  ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC
  LIMIT 1
}
```
